    ? "[Shell optimization: RTK]\n" +
      "rtk (Rust Token Killer) is installed. When using the shell tool, prefix commands with `rtk` for compressed output:\n" +
      "  `rtk git status` / `rtk git diff` / `rtk git log` — compact git output\n" +
